Class CompletionAdapter

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.jface.text.contentassist.ICompletionListener, org.eclipse.jface.text.contentassist.ICompletionListenerExtension, org.eclipse.jface.text.contentassist.ICompletionListenerExtension2, Listener, CompletionListener, Registrable

    public class CompletionAdapter
extends Adapter
implements CompletionListener
    An abstract adapter class for a CompletionListener. The methods in this class are empty. This class exists as convenience for creating listener objects.

    Extend this class to create a CompletionListener and override the methods for the events of interest.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Pavol Zbell
